ig10001696\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001696\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1943-1944 99 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002000\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002000\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Agnello 1953 no.70 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002211\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002211\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Rizzone 2009 208 fig.3 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001635\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001635\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Rizzone 2009 56 no.6 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001633\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001633\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>quadrate epsilon; alpha tending to the cursive form, crossbar descending to lower left; uncial omega; quadrate lunate sigma.\u003C/p> Line 1-5  28  Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[243,246,249,252,255,258,261,264],{"id":244,"html":245},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/EPANRKPM\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/EPANRKPM\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>ἐτελεύτησ-\u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>εν \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀγάθη\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀγάθη\">Ἀγάθη\u003C/span>\u003C/span> χρη-\u003Cb