o dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2015-01-13\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic001635.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2015-01-13\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#JP\" source=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/EPANRKPM\">\n                \u003Cab>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>ἐτελεύτησ\n                    \u003Clb n=\"2\" break=\"no\"/>εν \u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>Ἀγάθη\u003C/name>\u003C/persName> χρη\n                    \u003Clb n=\"3\" break=\"no\"/>στιανὴ μηνὶ\n                    \u003Clb n=\"4\"/>μαίῳ ἀπὸ \u003Cexpan>\u003Cabbr>κ\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>α\u003C/ex>\u003Cabbr>\u003Chi rend=\"small\">λ\u003C/hi>\u003C/abbr>\u003Cex>ανδῶν\u003C/ex>\u003C/expan> \u003Cnum value=\"14\">ιδ\u003C/num>\n                    \u003Clb n=\"5\"/>λοιπὸν \u003Cnum value=\"17\">ιζ\u003C/num>\n                \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\u003Cnote>Text of Agnello 1953\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                    \u003Capp loc=\"3\">\u003Cnote>Rizzone: στιαν (η omitted by error?)\u003C/note>\u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                \u003Cp>Agathe, a Christian, died in the month of May, 14 (days) from the kalends, 17 (days) remaining (to the end of the month)\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\">\n                \u003Cp>The dating formula is unusual, but is attested in the Rabat catacomb in Malta (so Rizzone).\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\u003C!-- Note also Ferrua RAC 61 (1985) 70 n.12-->\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Agnello\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1953\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>no.70\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/D9BZFDDR\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002211\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002211\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Orsi\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1942\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>224 no.3\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/XXUZUPJI\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001696\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001696\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Ferrua\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1943-1944\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>99\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3TJW6Z56\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002000\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002000\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Rizzone\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2009\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>208 fig.3\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/EPANRKPM\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001635\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001635\u003C/ref>\n                    \u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Rizzone\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>2009\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>56 no.6\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/8ENX9UZ5\"/>\n                        \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001633\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001633\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n\t   \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\u003Cbibl/>\u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
